WEBVTT

1
00:52:36.870 --> 00:52:39.130 
航天局的聪明人给了我
the smart people at NASA have sent me instructions

2
00:52:39.140 --> 00:52:40.870 
如何黑进火星车的指令...
on how to hack the Rover...

3
00:52:40.870 --> 00:52:43.140 
用它跟探路者号通信
so that it can talk to Pathfinder.

4
00:52:43.140 --> 00:52:45.310 
只要我向火星车的操作系统内...
If I hack a tiny bit of code...

5
00:52:45.310 --> 00:52:48.540 
插入仅仅20个指令的一小段代码...
just 20 instructions in the Rover's operating system...

6
00:52:48.540 --> 00:52:50.080 
航天局就可以把火星车和探路者号的
NASA can link the Rover to Pathfinder's

7
00:52:50.080 --> 00:52:52.080 
广播频率连在一起...
broadcasting frequency...

8
00:52:52.080 --> 00:52:54.880 
我们就可以通话了
and we're in business.

